creator: Libaoo Apps
descriptionHtml:
Download the latest literary novelties and bestsellers from African and foreign authors. Browse your collection of books in your library and flip through books and comics with the touch of a button.

Are you new to Libaoo? Sign up for the best deal on digital books. *

Download our free app and get access to thousands of books for free or at affordable prices, often much cheaper than the print version. Find all the books you dream of, from the latest releases to the most essential classics.

The Libaoo app makes reading even easier and more convenient:

• Personalize the way you read. Enjoy crisp, crisp text in the size and font you want. Try Night Mode to make reading easier on your eyes before bed.

• Our easy-to-use and wonderfully well-designed reader lets you browse your eBook with your fingertips. No need to worry: you won't lose track and can even see how many pages you have left to read.

Discover personalized recommendations based on the digital books we think you will like. Read thousands of free eBook previews and find your next crush.

• Start playing on one device and resume on another. The Libaoo app remembers where you left off, so you can continue reading on all your devices.

• Share your love of reading on Facebook, Twitter and Instagram. Post your favorite quotes, notes and thoughts from your readings.

• Rate and rate the books you've read, or read reviews from other bibliophiles like you!

• Read in English, French, Spanish, Italian, German, Dutch, Portuguese and Brazilian Portuguese or Japanese.

* Digital books are available all over the world. You can play them on smartphones and tablets running Android version 4.4 or later.
